      "author": "github-actions[bot]",
      "description": "## What's changed\n\n### Bug fixes\n- Add `evt.defaultPrevented` guard to `editor-paste` handler (#13, PR #25)\n- Fix unsafe `any` type in `loadSettings` (#14, PR #25)\n- Replace `document.createDocumentFragment()` with `createFragment()` (#15, PR #25)\n- Use `activeDocument` instead of `document` for popout window compatibility (#16, PR #25)\n- Replace `createEl('span')` with `createSpan()` ×3 (#17, PR #25)\n- Pin `obsidian` dependency to `1.13.1` — prevents supply chain attacks (#18, PR #26)\n- Commit `package-lock.json` for reproducible builds (#19, PR #26)\n- Remove zip artifact from release assets — only `main.js`, `manifest.json`, `styles.css` (#20, PR #27)\n- Align `package.json` license field with GPL-3.0 `LICENSE` file (#23, PR #24)\n\n### Improvements\n- Add GitHub artifact attestation for `main.js` (#21, PR #27)\n- Add automated CI release workflow (`.github/workflows/release.yml`)\n- Resolve manifest name mismatch — plugin now registered as 'Media Embed' (#22)",
